
  Umbra OS — hardened Debian with an opsec layer.

  ★ Security command center ....  umbra          (run it for the full menu)

  Common:
    umbra audit .......... full audit (verify + rootkit + integrity + updates)
    umbra net ............ network exposure (IP, MAC, DNS, ports, Tor)
    umbra scan <path> .... malware scan (ClamAV)
    umbra tor on ......... route all traffic through Tor (kill-switch)
    umbra scrub <file> ... strip metadata before sharing
    umbra panic .......... emergency: cut net, wipe keys, power off

  Controls & trade-offs documented in /usr/share/doc/umbra/.

